<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Not Found - Furni</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #3c5c4b;
            padding: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            color: white;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .nav-item {
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            color: #f9ca24;
        }
        
        .error-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 300px);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3c5c4b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #3c5c4b;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .error-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .home-button {
            background-color: #3c5c4b;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        
        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #2c4c3b;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .shop-button {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #3c5c4b;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border: 2px solid #3c5c4b;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .shop-button:hover {
            background-color: #3c5c4b;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .furniture-image {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #3c5c4b;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-menu {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .error-code {
                font-size: 80px;
            }
            
            .error-message {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .furniture-image {
                max-width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="navbar">
                <a href="/" class="logo">UrbenNest.</a>
                
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section class="error-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
                <h2 class="error-message">Page Not Found</h2>
                <p class="error-description">
                    We're sorry, but the page you're looking for doesn't seem to exist. 
                    Perhaps you've mistyped the URL or the page has been moved.
                </p>
                <div class="error-actions">
                    <a href="/" class="home-button">Back to Home</a>
                    <a href="/shop" class="shop-button">Continue Shopping</a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
   
</body>
</html>